# Privacy Policy for 木西app

**Effective Date:** April 9th, 2025  
**Last Updated:** April 9th, 2005  

Thank you for using **木西app**. Your privacy is important to us. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your personal information when you use our app.  

## 1. Information We Collect  
We may collect the following types of information:  

- **Personal Information:** When you create an account, we may collect your name, email address, and profile details.  
- **Usage Data:** We collect data about how you interact with the app, such as features used and time spent.  
- **Device Information:** We may collect device type, operating system, and other technical details.  

## 2. How We Use Your Information  
We use your data to:  

- Improve the app experience  
- Provide customer support  
- Monitor app performance and detect issues  
- Send updates and notifications (with your consent)  

## 3. Data Sharing and Security  
- We **do not sell** your personal data.  
- Data is encrypted and stored securely.  
- We may share anonymized data for analytics or legal reasons.  

## 4. Your Rights  
- You can update or delete your account at any time.  
- You can opt out of notifications and data collection in settings.  
- Contact us for any data-related requests.  

## 5. Contact Us  
If you have any questions, please contact us at **[your email or GitHub Issues page]**.  
